00:12:07.760 --> 00:12:11.610 align:middle line:84%
and we begin living by its
more righteous or upright

00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:15.930 align:middle line:84%
directions rather than
our lower earthly self.

00:12:15.930 --> 00:12:19.610 align:middle line:84%
Have you ever seen your higher
self or connected with it?

00:12:19.610 --> 00:12:21.910 align:middle line:84%
I was given a possible
glimpse of my higher self

00:12:21.910 --> 00:12:24.170 align:middle line:90%
in January, 1999.

00:12:24.170 --> 00:12:26.780 align:middle line:84%
I had given a presentation
in Memphis, Tennessee.

00:12:26.780 --> 00:12:30.160 align:middle line:84%
And afterward, some of the group
went out for dinner together.

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:32.440 align:middle line:84%
A woman was sitting
across the table from me,

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:34.870 align:middle line:90%
and she was staring through me.

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:37.650 align:middle line:84%
And she was concealing a
drawing that she was making.

00:12:37.650 --> 00:12:40.240 align:middle line:84%
And finally, she
produced the drawing.

00:12:40.240 --> 00:12:42.600 align:middle line:84%
This is your higher
self, she said.

00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:45.040 align:middle line:90%
And I was kind of blown away.

00:12:45.040 --> 00:12:47.370 align:middle line:84%
The three sacred
nuts, she said, were

00:12:47.370 --> 00:12:48.890 align:middle line:90%
a part of my consciousness.

00:12:48.890 --> 00:12:50.670 align:middle line:84%
But she didn't know
what they meant.

00:12:50.670 --> 00:12:54.580 align:middle line:84%
So was the related symbol
that looked like a trident.

00:12:54.580 --> 00:12:56.820 align:middle line:84%
It took me a number of
years, but I finally

00:12:56.820 --> 00:13:00.270 align:middle line:84%
learned that the trident is the
symbol for an instrument that

00:13:00.270 --> 00:13:02.700 align:middle line:90%
opens the gates of heaven.

00:13:02.700 --> 00:13:04.740 align:middle line:84%
And those three
sacred nuts, they

00:13:04.740 --> 00:13:06.290 align:middle line:84%
symbolize what
the Buddhists call

00:13:06.290 --> 00:13:08.790 align:middle line:90%
the Chintamani of the Buddha.

00:13:08.790 --> 00:13:11.740 align:middle line:84%
They are the three seeds
of the awakened soul

00:13:11.740 --> 00:13:15.590 align:middle line:84%
that produce the light body, or
sheer garment, he is wearing.

00:13:15.590 --> 00:13:20.810 align:middle line:84%
So did my higher self
reveal itself to this woman?

00:13:20.810 --> 00:13:21.910 align:middle line:90%
Who knows?

00:13:21.910 --> 00:13:24.940 align:middle line:84%
But maybe the future
me, like the future you,

00:13:24.940 --> 00:13:28.140 align:middle line:84%
was leaving clues,
like ET leaving

00:13:28.140 --> 00:13:31.230 align:middle line:90%
Reese's Pieces for Elliott.

00:13:31.230 --> 00:13:33.980 align:middle line:84%
The beautiful Indian
expression, "Namaste,"

00:13:33.980 --> 00:13:38.530 align:middle line:84%
acknowledges the divine
spark or spirit force within.

00:13:38.530 --> 00:13:41.020 align:middle line:84%
To perform Namaste, we
place the hands together

00:13:41.020 --> 00:13:45.880 align:middle line:84%
at the heart chakra, close
the eyes, and bow the head.

00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:48.320 align:middle line:84%
It can also be done by
placing the hands together

00:13:48.320 --> 00:13:51.210 align:middle line:84%
in front of the third
eye, bowing the head,

00:13:51.210 --> 00:13:54.390 align:middle line:84%
and then bringing the
hands down to the heart.

00:13:54.390 --> 00:13:58.140 align:middle line:84%
This is a spiritually-deep
practice of respect.

00:13:58.140 --> 00:14:00.930 align:middle line:84%
The hands on the heart
chakra increase the flow

00:14:00.930 --> 00:14:03.740 align:middle line:84%
of divine love, the
spirit, without which

00:14:03.740 --> 00:14:05.490 align:middle line:90%
nothing is possible.

00:14:05.490 --> 00:14:09.290 align:middle line:84%
Bowing the head to show our
crown and closing the eyes

00:14:09.290 --> 00:14:12.910 align:middle line:84%
helps the mind surrender to
the divine spark, the soul,

00:14:12.910 --> 00:14:16.100 align:middle line:84%
in the heart and merges
with the third eye.

00:14:16.100 --> 00:14:19.730 align:middle line:84%
It frees us from the body
and acknowledges the eternity

00:14:19.730 --> 00:14:22.820 align:middle line:84%
of the soul and connects
us to its origin

00:14:22.820 --> 00:14:25.140 align:middle line:90%
in the timeless realm.

00:14:25.140 --> 00:14:28.350 align:middle line:84%
In the Gnostic traditions,
which come from India,

00:14:28.350 --> 00:14:30.620 align:middle line:84%
the purpose of life is
to enable the divine

00:14:30.620 --> 00:14:34.720 align:middle line:84%
spark to be released from
its imprisonment in matter

00:14:34.720 --> 00:14:39.840 align:middle line:84%
and return to God or the divine
light, the timeless realm.

00:14:39.840 --> 00:14:41.910 align:middle line:84%
In the Dead Sea
Scrolls, the Essenes

00:14:41.910 --> 00:14:45.395 align:middle line:84%
expressed the concept of
Namaste in ascension this way.

00:14:45.395 --> 00:14:48.110 align:middle line:84%
May you be as an
angel of the presence

00:14:48.110 --> 00:14:51.770 align:middle line:84%
and the abode of holiness
to the glory of God.

00:14:51.770 --> 00:14:54.090 align:middle line:84%
May you be as an
angel of the presence

00:14:54.090 --> 00:14:56.820 align:middle line:84%
in the abode of holiness
to the glory of God.

00:14:56.820 --> 00:15:00.650 align:middle line:84%
That really sets a
powerful intention.

00:15:00.650 --> 00:15:03.360 align:middle line:84%
It says we want
to become angels.

00:15:03.360 --> 00:15:05.505 align:middle line:84%
In the Gnostic, Christian,
and Essene tradition,

00:15:05.505 --> 00:15:08.200 align:middle line:84%
the cosmic Christ
is seen as an avatar

00:15:08.200 --> 00:15:12.060 align:middle line:84%
of light, which is taken
human form in order to lead

00:15:12.060 --> 00:15:14.840 align:middle line:90%
human souls back to the light.

00:15:14.840 --> 00:15:18.130 align:middle line:84%
There is a competition
for our souls.

00:15:18.130 --> 00:15:21.140 align:middle line:84%
Christianity refers to the
body made by the divine

00:15:21.140 --> 00:15:23.890 align:middle line:84%
spark as the temple
of the Holy Spirit.

00:15:23.890 --> 00:15:26.000 align:middle line:90%
Your body is the temple.

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:31.170 align:middle line:84%
The soul is the Holy Spirit
that the Hebrews called "I am."

00:15:31.170 --> 00:15:33.610 align:middle line:84%
Christianity brought
with it the idea

00:15:33.610 --> 00:15:37.240 align:middle line:84%
that both the soul
and the body it makes

00:15:37.240 --> 00:15:40.770 align:middle line:84%
will be raised together to
heaven at a future moment.

00:15:40.770 --> 00:15:43.260 align:middle line:84%
This resurrected
soul body is referred

00:15:43.260 --> 00:15:47.600 align:middle line:84%
to as a light body,
a soul light body

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:51.500 align:middle line:84%
that we will mirror
in our own ascension.

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:54.520 align:middle line:84%
When the Essene master John
the Baptist baptized Jesus,

00:15:54.520 --> 00:15:58.100 align:middle line:84%
he transmitted the Holy
Spirit in waves of light

00:15:58.100 --> 00:16:00.640 align:middle line:90%
into his open crown chakra.

00:16:00.640 --> 00:16:04.800 align:middle line:84%
He infused Jesus' body
with a light, a vibration,

00:16:04.800 --> 00:16:07.890 align:middle line:84%
that came from a
higher dimension.

00:16:07.890 --> 00:16:10.670 align:middle line:84%
The angels wait to give
the baptized Christ

00:16:10.670 --> 00:16:15.280 align:middle line:84%
his cloak of light, which is
called the robe of the soul,

00:16:15.280 --> 00:16:19.680 align:middle line:84%
and is worn by all the ascended
beings in the higher frequency

00:16:19.680 --> 00:16:20.950 align:middle line:90%
new world.

00:16:20.950 --> 00:16:23.310 align:middle line:90%
And it is our goal.

00:16:23.310 --> 00:16:26.710 align:middle line:84%
Acquiring this soul
garment is our life goal.

00:16:26.710 --> 00:16:31.920 align:middle line:84%
And our soul uses it to
open doors to other realms.

00:16:31.920 --> 00:16:34.410 align:middle line:84%
Just as a person
changes his clothes,

00:16:34.410 --> 00:16:38.020 align:middle line:84%
our soul can change our
body from incarnation

00:16:38.020 --> 00:16:39.910 align:middle line:90%
to incarnation.

00:16:39.910 --> 00:16:44.670 align:middle line:84%
We can rearrange the molecules
and change our soul clothes.

00:16:44.670 --> 00:16:48.040 align:middle line:84%
Jesus' soul transfiguration,
a metamorphosis,

00:16:48.040 --> 00:16:51.060 align:middle line:84%
demonstrated that our
body is transformable.

00:16:51.060 --> 00:16:54.620 align:middle line:84%
Though a divine spark,
the soul is redeemable.

00:16:54.620 --> 00:16:55.420 align:middle line:90%
It's immortal.

00:16:55.420 --> 00:16:58.870 align:middle line:84%
It comes from the
stars, and we literally

00:16:58.870 --> 00:17:02.540 align:middle line:90%
are truly made of star stuff.

00:17:02.540 --> 00:17:06.050 align:middle line:84%
Every single atom of our body,
except hydrogen and traces

00:17:06.050 --> 00:17:09.579 align:middle line:84%
of other light elements,
was formed in a supernova.

00:17:09.579 --> 00:17:16.210 align:middle line:84%
When a star explodes, it briefly
changes into a butterfly form.

00:17:16.210 --> 00:17:18.290 align:middle line:84%
This is another reason
why the butterfly

00:17:18.290 --> 00:17:23.589 align:middle line:84%
is one of the more profound
symbols for the awakened soul.

00:17:23.589 --> 00:17:27.119 align:middle line:84%
As Jesus taught, loving
actions awaken the soul

00:17:27.119 --> 00:17:30.570 align:middle line:84%
and produce bright white
clothes for the soul.

00:17:30.570 --> 00:17:34.910 align:middle line:84%
This is the White Tara
radiating her light body.

00:17:34.910 --> 00:17:38.970 align:middle line:84%
Buddhism teaches that we can
transform our world and ascend

00:17:38.970 --> 00:17:42.440 align:middle line:84%
to a purer place by
purifying our soul.

00:17:42.440 --> 00:17:46.020 align:middle line:84%
We do this by changing
the actions of our lives

00:17:46.020 --> 00:17:48.540 align:middle line:90%
from the inside out.

00:17:48.540 --> 00:17:51.360 align:middle line:84%
Just as 90% of losing
weight is about what

00:17:51.360 --> 00:17:54.690 align:middle line:84%
you put in your mouth,
90% of ascension

00:17:54.690 --> 00:17:57.080 align:middle line:84%
is about what comes
out of your heart.

00:17:57.080 --> 00:17:59.290 align:middle line:84%
Ascension and
attaining a light body

00:17:59.290 --> 00:18:04.040 align:middle line:84%
is about what you do or
don't do in each moment.

00:18:04.040 --> 00:18:06.890 align:middle line:84%
In addition to loving
actions, another way

00:18:06.890 --> 00:18:09.150 align:middle line:84%
the Gnostics and Buddhists
teach us to do this

00:18:09.150 --> 00:18:11.810 align:middle line:84%
is through contemplation
of sacred images

00:18:11.810 --> 00:18:14.040 align:middle line:90%
of soul transfiguration.

00:18:14.040 --> 00:18:16.370 align:middle line:84%
My wife Clare hosted
a series on Gaiam

00:18:16.370 --> 00:18:18.820 align:middle line:84%
called "Arcanum,"
in which we explored

00:18:18.820 --> 00:18:23.180 align:middle line:84%
the power of sacred art to
illuminate and enlighten us.

00:18:23.180 --> 00:18:27.540 align:middle line:84%
In Buddhism, this is a sacred
practice, called ekagrata,

00:18:27.540 --> 00:18:31.780 align:middle line:84%
or one point of focus
on sacred images.

00:18:31.780 --> 00:18:35.450 align:middle line:84%
The idea is that is that as
we connect with the images,

00:18:35.450 --> 00:18:39.930 align:middle line:84%
we become them as we actually
are one with everything

00:18:39.930 --> 00:18:42.610 align:middle line:90%
always in any way.

00:18:42.610 --> 00:18:44.470 align:middle line:84%
According to
Buddhism, each of us

00:18:44.470 --> 00:18:46.930 align:middle line:84%
holds within an
exhaustless source

00:18:46.930 --> 00:18:50.140 align:middle line:90%
of compassion and wisdom.

00:18:50.140 --> 00:18:54.860 align:middle line:84%
All we need to do is to connect
with our most essential nature,

00:18:54.860 --> 00:18:57.920 align:middle line:84%
our light body, that
has been covered over

00:18:57.920 --> 00:19:02.170 align:middle line:84%
by negative emotions
and false perceptions.

00:19:02.170 --> 00:19:06.180 align:middle line:84%
There are many ways to remind
ourselves of them, among them

00:19:06.180 --> 00:19:09.940 align:middle line:84%
are meditation, prayers,
yoga, recitation of mantras,

00:19:09.940 --> 00:19:14.300 align:middle line:84%
construction of inspiring
places, visiting sacred places.

00:19:14.300 --> 00:19:17.702 align:middle line:84%
But in Buddhism, there is
especially open eye meditations

00:19:17.702 --> 00:19:20.690 align:middle line:84%
on light body
images such as this,

00:19:20.690 --> 00:19:25.630 align:middle line:84%
which portray the state of being
of the ascended human form.

00:19:25.630 --> 00:19:30.400 align:middle line:84%
Sacred images play our
DNA like we play a piano.

00:19:30.400 --> 00:19:34.920 align:middle line:84%
And as we contemplate, meditate,
and reflect on the images,

00:19:34.920 --> 00:19:40.000 align:middle line:84%
we begin to mirror them
from the inside out.

00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:42.400 align:middle line:84%
This is based on the
Egyptian practice of making

00:19:42.400 --> 00:19:44.790 align:middle line:90%
magically active images.

00:19:44.790 --> 00:19:48.110 align:middle line:84%
So long as an action was seen
performed on the temple walls,

00:19:48.110 --> 00:19:50.540 align:middle line:90%
it existed into eternity.

00:19:50.540 --> 00:19:52.690 align:middle line:84%
This is why the early
Christians hacked out

00:19:52.690 --> 00:19:55.710 align:middle line:84%
the body parts of the Pharaohs
and severed the connection

00:19:55.710 --> 00:19:57.710 align:middle line:90%
with the divine realm.

00:19:57.710 --> 00:20:01.170 align:middle line:84%
One of our jobs is to
reassemble the lost connection

00:20:01.170 --> 00:20:05.280 align:middle line:84%
to the sacred imagination,
the mind of the soul.

00:20:05.280 --> 00:20:07.710 align:middle line:84%
I am personally
astounded by the power

00:20:07.710 --> 00:20:10.360 align:middle line:84%
of the soul, the awakened
soul and the power

00:20:10.360 --> 00:20:13.120 align:middle line:90%
of images to activate the soul.

00:20:13.120 --> 00:20:16.240 align:middle line:84%
Like the Egyptians and Gnostics,
Buddhist ascension teachings

00:20:16.240 --> 00:20:21.020 align:middle line:84%
say that paintings can become
portals to the afterlife realm.

00:20:21.020 --> 00:20:24.400 align:middle line:84%
To give you an example, one
of my favorite examples,

00:20:24.400 --> 00:20:26.680 align:middle line:84%
let's take a look at this
welcoming descent painting,

00:20:26.680 --> 00:20:30.150 align:middle line:84%
like this one, which were
indispensable religious

00:20:30.150 --> 00:20:33.080 align:middle line:84%
furnishings at
the time of death.

00:20:33.080 --> 00:20:35.410 align:middle line:84%
Such paintings depict
the scene in which

00:20:35.410 --> 00:20:37.990 align:middle line:84%
the Amida Buddha
and his attendants

00:20:37.990 --> 00:20:42.340 align:middle line:84%
descend from heaven on clouds
to take a believing soul back

00:20:42.340 --> 00:20:47.380 align:middle line:84%
to the Western paradise, where
pure land and the lotus throne.

00:20:47.380 --> 00:20:51.080 align:middle line:84%
The scrolls were often hung
by or beside the bedside

00:20:51.080 --> 00:20:54.450 align:middle line:84%
of the dying to ensure
the prospect of rebirth

00:20:54.450 --> 00:20:56.020 align:middle line:90%
in paradise.

00:20:56.020 --> 00:20:58.590 align:middle line:84%
Since traditionally, the
dying lay with their heads

00:20:58.590 --> 00:21:01.240 align:middle line:84%
to the north and their
faces turned west,

00:21:01.240 --> 00:21:03.600 align:middle line:84%
welcoming descent
paintings usually

00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:06.650 align:middle line:84%
depict the Buddha
and his entourage

00:21:06.650 --> 00:21:10.340 align:middle line:84%
coming from the upper left
down to the lower right

00:21:10.340 --> 00:21:13.120 align:middle line:84%
so as to meet the
gaze of the dying.

00:21:13.120 --> 00:21:17.110 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes, silken cords were
attached to the Buddhist's

00:21:17.110 --> 00:21:21.670 align:middle line:84%
hand, offering the dying
physical assistance

00:21:21.670 --> 00:21:23.575 align:middle line:90%
during the journey to paradise.

00:21:23.575 --> 00:21:37.240 align:middle line:90%


00:21:37.240 --> 00:21:40.970 align:middle line:84%
Did you know that
until 1926, humans

00:21:40.970 --> 00:21:44.230 align:middle line:84%
believed we lived in a celestial
egg, our Milky Way galaxy,

00:21:44.230 --> 00:21:48.650 align:middle line:84%
and that it was the
entirety of the universe?

00:21:48.650 --> 00:21:49.680 align:middle line:90%
That's right.

00:21:49.680 --> 00:21:52.750 align:middle line:84%
Until 100 years ago,
humanity thought

00:21:52.750 --> 00:21:56.920 align:middle line:84%
the entire universe was
comprised of only the stars we

00:21:56.920 --> 00:21:58.790 align:middle line:90%
see in the night sky.

00:21:58.790 --> 00:22:00.760 align:middle line:84%
In fact, when we look
into the night sky,

00:22:00.760 --> 00:22:04.290 align:middle line:84%
all the stars we see are in
the yellow dot in this image.

00:22:04.290 --> 00:22:05.680 align:middle line:90%
That's it.

00:22:05.680 --> 00:22:09.440 align:middle line:84%
There's obviously a
lot more out there.

00:22:09.440 --> 00:22:12.410 align:middle line:84%
Then, Hubble began looking
at photographs of the night

00:22:12.410 --> 00:22:15.470 align:middle line:84%
sky that showed cloudy
patches, called nebulae,

00:22:15.470 --> 00:22:18.630 align:middle line:90%
or interstellar clouds of dust.

00:22:18.630 --> 00:22:21.640 align:middle line:84%
Most of Hubble's colleagues at
the Mount Wilson Observatory

00:22:21.640 --> 00:22:23.450 align:middle line:84%
thought these
fuzzy eggs of light

00:22:23.450 --> 00:22:25.300 align:middle line:90%
were all in the Milky Way.

00:22:25.300 --> 00:22:27.220 align:middle line:90%
But Hubble didn't think so.

00:22:27.220 --> 00:22:31.080 align:middle line:84%
Hubble answered the question by
taking the best possible photos

00:22:31.080 --> 00:22:33.610 align:middle line:84%
of these fuzzy eggs
and proved that they

00:22:33.610 --> 00:22:38.030 align:middle line:84%
were outside and
beyond the Milky Way.

00:22:38.030 --> 00:22:42.265 align:middle line:84%
The cloudy egg of light
was a whole other galaxy,

00:22:42.265 --> 00:22:47.610 align:middle line:84%
and we named the newly
discovered galaxy Andromeda.

00:22:47.610 --> 00:22:50.890 align:middle line:84%
She was named after the
goddess in Greek mythology

00:22:50.890 --> 00:22:53.910 align:middle line:84%
who was chained naked
to a rock as a sacrifice

00:22:53.910 --> 00:22:58.970 align:middle line:84%
to the sea monster Cetus but
was saved from death by Perseus,

00:22:58.970 --> 00:23:04.670 align:middle line:84%
who rides in on his flying
white horse of light.

00:23:04.670 --> 00:23:06.750 align:middle line:84%
Hubble's discovery
led to the realization

00:23:06.750 --> 00:23:10.310 align:middle line:84%
that our galaxy is a
sister galaxy to hundreds

00:23:10.310 --> 00:23:15.670 align:middle line:84%
of billions of galaxies that
inhabit the known universe.

00:23:15.670 --> 00:23:20.610 align:middle line:84%
More, Hubble proved our
universe is expanding.

00:23:20.610 --> 00:23:25.080 align:middle line:10%
And this realization led
scientists to seek and discover

00:23:25.080 --> 00:23:28.390 align:middle line:10%
the origins of the universe.

00:23:28.390 --> 00:23:32.320 align:middle line:84%
Hubble's discovery completely
shattered our understanding

00:23:32.320 --> 00:23:36.830 align:middle line:84%
of existence by increasing
the size of the known universe

00:23:36.830 --> 00:23:40.420 align:middle line:84%
many, many times
over, Hubble took us

00:23:40.420 --> 00:23:46.530 align:middle line:84%
into the soul's true garden
and closer to our origins.

00:23:46.530 --> 00:23:49.890 align:middle line:84%
His discovery cracked
open the cosmic egg.

00:23:49.890 --> 00:23:54.470 align:middle line:84%
And it was humanity's
Great Awakening.

00:23:54.470 --> 00:23:56.860 align:middle line:10%
In the 1950s, the
Gaia Hypothesis

00:23:56.860 --> 00:24:00.010 align:middle line:10%
proposed our Mother Earth
is a conscious being.

00:24:00.010 --> 00:24:04.900 align:middle line:84%
And all of its life functions
as an organic whole.

