In 2013, NASA validated
the Quran's assertion

00:24:08.470 --> 00:24:12.250 align:middle line:10%
that the earth is
actually egg-shaped.

00:24:12.250 --> 00:24:16.570 align:middle line:84%
So if the person is a conscious,
living and loving being,

00:24:16.570 --> 00:24:18.840 align:middle line:90%
how about our galaxy?

00:24:18.840 --> 00:24:22.890 align:middle line:84%
What if it, too, is
a conscious entity?

00:24:22.890 --> 00:24:26.990 align:middle line:84%
Can our galaxy be viewed as
a divine spark or cosmic egg

00:24:26.990 --> 00:24:30.680 align:middle line:84%
in a greater body of souls,
just as our soul is a divine

00:24:30.680 --> 00:24:33.570 align:middle line:90%
spark in our galaxy?

00:24:33.570 --> 00:24:36.340 align:middle line:90%
The answer is yes.

00:24:36.340 --> 00:24:39.850 align:middle line:84%
For we now know
that our galaxy is

00:24:39.850 --> 00:24:45.150 align:middle line:84%
one of 100,000 galaxies in
what is known as the Laniakea

00:24:45.150 --> 00:24:47.535 align:middle line:90%
Supercluster of Galaxies.

00:24:47.535 --> 00:24:51.740 align:middle line:10%
But this is only a tiny fraction
of the universe's estimated

00:24:51.740 --> 00:24:57.060 align:middle line:10%
total of 125 billion galaxies.

00:24:57.060 --> 00:25:03.040 align:middle line:10%
Laniakea is a Hawaiian word
meaning "immeasurable heaven."

00:25:03.040 --> 00:25:05.760 align:middle line:84%
The Hubble Space
Telescope opened a gateway

00:25:05.760 --> 00:25:08.090 align:middle line:90%
to this "immeasurable heaven."

00:25:08.090 --> 00:25:12.480 align:middle line:84%
And I've always loved the word
play or pun in the name Hubble.

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:14.540 align:middle line:90%
"Hu" means God.

00:25:14.540 --> 00:25:16.850 align:middle line:84%
And with the addition
of a letter "a,"

00:25:16.850 --> 00:25:19.950 align:middle line:84%
the "bble" becomes
"Bable," the name

00:25:19.950 --> 00:25:23.920 align:middle line:84%
of the ladder or gate to
God in the pivotal story

00:25:23.920 --> 00:25:26.080 align:middle line:90%
of the book of Genesis.

00:25:26.080 --> 00:25:30.500 align:middle line:84%
The Tower of Babel was
located in ancient Babylon,

00:25:30.500 --> 00:25:34.180 align:middle line:84%
which was associated with
lust and prostitution.

00:25:34.180 --> 00:25:36.770 align:middle line:84%
The funny thing is, when
Hubble discovered the Andromeda

00:25:36.770 --> 00:25:41.260 align:middle line:84%
galaxy, he did so while peering
through the Hooker Space

00:25:41.260 --> 00:25:42.910 align:middle line:90%
Telescope.

00:25:42.910 --> 00:25:47.200 align:middle line:84%
The universe definitely
has a sense of humor.

00:25:47.200 --> 00:25:50.990 align:middle line:84%
In the book of Genesis, the
Old Testament God Yahweh

00:25:50.990 --> 00:25:55.200 align:middle line:84%
destroyed the Tower of Babel,
fearing that with this ladder,

00:25:55.200 --> 00:25:59.720 align:middle line:84%
nothing would be
impossible for humanity.

00:25:59.720 --> 00:26:02.940 align:middle line:84%
The Hubble Space Telescope
clearly opened a gate

00:26:02.940 --> 00:26:09.290 align:middle line:84%
to the stars, a stargate in
our consciousness, a soul gate.

00:26:09.290 --> 00:26:14.630 align:middle line:84%
Now, perhaps nothing will
be impossible for us.

00:26:14.630 --> 00:26:17.050 align:middle line:84%
Actually, watching
that Billy Meier video

00:26:17.050 --> 00:26:18.920 align:middle line:90%
wasn't my first awakening.

00:26:18.920 --> 00:26:22.330 align:middle line:84%
I had spent part of the
1980s doing private research

00:26:22.330 --> 00:26:24.860 align:middle line:84%
for a self-help guru,
answering questions

00:26:24.860 --> 00:26:26.600 align:middle line:90%
like, how does the brain work.

00:26:26.600 --> 00:26:28.070 align:middle line:90%
Why do people fail?

00:26:28.070 --> 00:26:29.510 align:middle line:90%
What is culture?

00:26:29.510 --> 00:26:31.410 align:middle line:90%
Why do people gain weight?

00:26:31.410 --> 00:26:35.510 align:middle line:84%
It was an amazing educational
experience for me.

00:26:35.510 --> 00:26:38.540 align:middle line:84%
I didn't realize it at the
time, but this research

00:26:38.540 --> 00:26:42.350 align:middle line:84%
was preparing me for
my own soul awakening.

00:26:42.350 --> 00:26:45.430 align:middle line:84%
This came when I entered a
literary contest, sponsored

00:26:45.430 --> 00:26:48.810 align:middle line:84%
by media mogul Ted Turner,
who was seeking answers

00:26:48.810 --> 00:26:50.790 align:middle line:90%
to our world's problems.

00:26:50.790 --> 00:26:55.180 align:middle line:84%
In 1989, Turner said that
science and technology can't

00:26:55.180 --> 00:26:57.230 align:middle line:90%
solve the world's problems.

00:26:57.230 --> 00:27:01.620 align:middle line:10%
And he offered $500,000 for the
best piece of fiction dealing

00:27:01.620 --> 00:27:04.460 align:middle line:10%
with themes ensuring the
survival and prosperity

00:27:04.460 --> 00:27:06.680 align:middle line:10%
of all life on Earth.

00:27:06.680 --> 00:27:09.320 align:middle line:84%
My story was called
"Turtle Island."

00:27:09.320 --> 00:27:12.290 align:middle line:84%
It was based on my
previous research.

00:27:12.290 --> 00:27:16.080 align:middle line:84%
It focused on a sage's dream
to build an academy where

00:27:16.080 --> 00:27:18.545 align:middle line:84%
the children of the world
would gather to learn to build

00:27:18.545 --> 00:27:21.140 align:middle line:90%
a new human civilization.

00:27:21.140 --> 00:27:23.776 align:middle line:90%
I named this school "Tula."

00:27:23.776 --> 00:27:25.400 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know where
the name came from.

00:27:25.400 --> 00:27:28.580 align:middle line:84%
It just popped into my head,
and it sounded really nice.

00:27:28.580 --> 00:27:32.990 align:middle line:84%
And in my story, Tula was the
largest man-made structure

00:27:32.990 --> 00:27:37.220 align:middle line:84%
on Earth, so large it could
be a seen from Earth's orbit.

00:27:37.220 --> 00:27:40.425 align:middle line:84%
It was shaped like an egg,
with butterfly-shaped wings

00:27:40.425 --> 00:27:42.500 align:middle line:90%
and a heart-shaped head.

00:27:42.500 --> 00:27:45.180 align:middle line:84%
These are the symbols
of rebirth, renewal,

00:27:45.180 --> 00:27:48.130 align:middle line:90%
and regeneration and the soul.

00:27:48.130 --> 00:27:50.830 align:middle line:84%
I actually pulled these
symbols off the glass doors

00:27:50.830 --> 00:27:52.790 align:middle line:90%
leading into my study.

00:27:52.790 --> 00:27:56.110 align:middle line:84%
And in my story,
this giant structure

00:27:56.110 --> 00:27:58.730 align:middle line:84%
was meant to be interpreted
by otherworldly beings

00:27:58.730 --> 00:28:01.660 align:middle line:84%
as a sign of our
civilization's advancement,

00:28:01.660 --> 00:28:04.920 align:middle line:84%
sort of like the Batman symbol
in the sky, if you will.

00:28:04.920 --> 00:28:09.580 align:middle line:84%
But I was soon in
for a huge surprise.

00:28:09.580 --> 00:28:13.940 align:middle line:84%
I learned that Tula actually
existed in the ancient world.

00:28:13.940 --> 00:28:15.650 align:middle line:84%
In fact, it was the
name of the temple

00:28:15.650 --> 00:28:18.960 align:middle line:84%
of the Aztec god Quetzalcoatl,
the winged or feathered

00:28:18.960 --> 00:28:20.380 align:middle line:90%
serpent.

00:28:20.380 --> 00:28:24.150 align:middle line:84%
Tula was also the name
of the central healing

00:28:24.150 --> 00:28:27.270 align:middle line:84%
sun, or the "spiritual
son" as the ancients

00:28:27.270 --> 00:28:30.430 align:middle line:84%
called it, the Golden
Womb, from whence

00:28:30.430 --> 00:28:34.780 align:middle line:84%
the ancients believed all our
souls originated and remain

00:28:34.780 --> 00:28:39.400 align:middle line:84%
connected to and
ultimately will return to.

00:28:39.400 --> 00:28:43.920 align:middle line:84%
The ancient sources said that
this place, Tula, feeds us

00:28:43.920 --> 00:28:49.750 align:middle line:84%
with a cosmic essence, a
healing wisdom, rays, or waters.

00:28:49.750 --> 00:28:54.540 align:middle line:84%
And our sun is a gateway
for this cosmic energy

00:28:54.540 --> 00:28:56.980 align:middle line:90%
that feeds the soul.

00:28:56.980 --> 00:29:01.170 align:middle line:84%
It was incredible to me that I
pulled a name out of thin air,

00:29:01.170 --> 00:29:04.460 align:middle line:84%
and it happened to be the name
of the place our souls came

00:29:04.460 --> 00:29:05.490 align:middle line:90%
from.

00:29:05.490 --> 00:29:10.900 align:middle line:84%
The soul loves synchronicity
or remembering, right.

00:29:10.900 --> 00:29:14.820 align:middle line:84%
This discovery set me off to
learn more about the Milky Way.

00:29:14.820 --> 00:29:18.285 align:middle line:84%
We all have much to remember
about our cosmic egg, our home

00:29:18.285 --> 00:29:20.690 align:middle line:90%
galaxy, the Milky Way.

00:29:20.690 --> 00:29:23.200 align:middle line:84%
Many ancient traditions
regard the Milky Way

00:29:23.200 --> 00:29:27.980 align:middle line:84%
as the pathway built by
the gods, which souls

00:29:27.980 --> 00:29:30.860 align:middle line:90%
follow to the other world.

00:29:30.860 --> 00:29:34.200 align:middle line:84%
At the end of this path
lies the land of the dead,

00:29:34.200 --> 00:29:38.190 align:middle line:84%
which is viewed as a return to
greater life from the soul's

00:29:38.190 --> 00:29:39.810 align:middle line:90%
perspective.

00:29:39.810 --> 00:29:44.150 align:middle line:84%
In 500 BC, the Greek
philosopher Pythagoras

00:29:44.150 --> 00:29:47.572 align:middle line:84%
taught that our souls dwell
in the waters of the Milky

00:29:47.572 --> 00:29:51.340 align:middle line:84%
Way between
incarnations, inferring

00:29:51.340 --> 00:29:55.180 align:middle line:84%
that when we incarnate
on Earth, we each

00:29:55.180 --> 00:30:00.220 align:middle line:84%
bring a ray of the
healing sun with us.

00:30:00.220 --> 00:30:02.800 align:middle line:84%
Astrophysicist Dr.
Paul LaViolette

00:30:02.800 --> 00:30:06.400 align:middle line:84%
traced these myths and the
source of these healing waters,

00:30:06.400 --> 00:30:10.160 align:middle line:84%
the source of our soul, to the
black hole at our cosmic egg

00:30:10.160 --> 00:30:11.740 align:middle line:90%
center.

00:30:11.740 --> 00:30:14.580 align:middle line:84%
The black hole is seen
in this NASA image

00:30:14.580 --> 00:30:16.920 align:middle line:84%
as a bright white
spot surrounded

00:30:16.920 --> 00:30:20.300 align:middle line:90%
by beautiful ethereal purple.

00:30:20.300 --> 00:30:24.140 align:middle line:90%
Is this the source of our souls?

00:30:24.140 --> 00:30:27.750 align:middle line:84%
Is it possible that the ancients
had a source of knowledge

00:30:27.750 --> 00:30:29.170 align:middle line:90%
beyond our science?

00:30:29.170 --> 00:30:32.670 align:middle line:84%
Could it be they knew the
secrets of the soul's origin

00:30:32.670 --> 00:30:38.480 align:middle line:84%
itself, and we are now
rediscovering that source?

00:30:38.480 --> 00:30:42.515 align:middle line:84%
In 2010, NASA discovered
that a pillar of gamma rays

00:30:42.515 --> 00:30:45.770 align:middle line:84%
is spewing from the
galactic center.

00:30:45.770 --> 00:30:48.660 align:middle line:10%
For the first time,
human beings not only

00:30:48.660 --> 00:30:51.940 align:middle line:10%
grasped our place
within the Milky Way

00:30:51.940 --> 00:30:54.780 align:middle line:10%
but we also
potentially discovered

00:30:54.780 --> 00:30:57.750 align:middle line:10%
secrets about our
source, almost as

00:30:57.750 --> 00:31:01.230 align:middle line:10%
if we are being welcomed home.

00:31:01.230 --> 00:31:04.510 align:middle line:10%
So let's take a moment to
look at this incredible NASA

00:31:04.510 --> 00:31:06.940 align:middle line:10%
animation of our home galaxy.

00:31:06.940 --> 00:31:11.400 align:middle line:84%
It is truly awe-inspiring
and soul-tingling.

00:31:11.400 --> 00:31:14.440 align:middle line:84%
For generations, the
existence of this pillar

00:31:14.440 --> 00:31:18.300 align:middle line:84%
of light within the spinning
cosmic egg was unknown.

00:31:18.300 --> 00:31:21.006 align:middle line:84%
We have to ask, what
else is out there

00:31:21.006 --> 00:31:22.130 align:middle line:90%
that we have yet to detect?

00:31:22.130 --> 00:31:25.700 align:middle line:90%


00:31:25.700 --> 00:31:28.120 align:middle line:84%
My Turner Tomorrow
award experience

00:31:28.120 --> 00:31:31.170 align:middle line:84%
left me with the belief that
teaching children and all

00:31:31.170 --> 00:31:33.680 align:middle line:84%
of humanity about
the soul really

00:31:33.680 --> 00:31:36.220 align:middle line:84%
is the answer to our
world's problems.

00:31:36.220 --> 00:31:39.610 align:middle line:84%
We have to get beyond
the skin and see

00:31:39.610 --> 00:31:43.380 align:middle line:90%
the soul within everything.

00:31:43.380 --> 00:31:47.440 align:middle line:84%
Think about how different
our world, your world

00:31:47.440 --> 00:31:51.370 align:middle line:84%
would be if instead of just
being educated as a child,

00:31:51.370 --> 00:31:52.470 align:middle line:90%
you were also illuminated.

00:31:52.470 --> 00:31:55.410 align:middle line:90%


00:31:55.410 --> 00:31:57.920 align:middle line:84%
In the spring of 1991,
I read a wonderful book

00:31:57.920 --> 00:32:01.930 align:middle line:84%
called "Life Between Life" by
Joel Whitten and Joe Fisher.

00:32:01.930 --> 00:32:04.740 align:middle line:84%
This book dealt with
themes about reincarnation

00:32:04.740 --> 00:32:06.780 align:middle line:90%
and the other side.

00:32:06.780 --> 00:32:09.830 align:middle line:84%
The authors ask the
questions, what happens

00:32:09.830 --> 00:32:12.990 align:middle line:90%
during the space between lives.

00:32:12.990 --> 00:32:18.870 align:middle line:84%
Where do our souls reside when
we are not incarnated on Earth?

00:32:18.870 --> 00:32:22.810 align:middle line:84%
Where do we spend our
life between lives?

00:32:22.810 --> 00:32:27.140 align:middle line:84%
Is it spent in the Milky
Way as Pythagoras taught?

00:32:27.140 --> 00:32:29.680 align:middle line:84%
Where were you before
you came to Earth,

00:32:29.680 --> 00:32:32.530 align:middle line:84%
and where are you
going from here?

00:32:32.530 --> 00:32:34.440 align:middle line:84%
Have you ever
thought about this?

00:32:34.440 --> 00:32:36.020 align:middle line:90%
I know you have.

00:32:36.020 --> 00:32:38.320 align:middle line:90%
And what have you concluded?

00:32:38.320 --> 00:32:40.370 align:middle line:84%
Please share it with
us, if you would like.

00:32:40.370 --> 00:32:44.130 align:middle line:84%
It will help all
of us to remember.

00:32:44.130 --> 00:32:46.570 align:middle line:84%
The circumstantial evidence
presented in the book

00:32:46.570 --> 00:32:48.790 align:middle line:84%
suggests that our
soul evolution is

00:32:48.790 --> 00:32:53.380 align:middle line:84%
decided prior to entering into
another physical lifetime.

00:32:53.380 --> 00:32:56.350 align:middle line:84%
As people and situations
enter our lives,

00:32:56.350 --> 00:32:59.720 align:middle line:84%
we begin to understand
that these were preselected

00:32:59.720 --> 00:33:02.340 align:middle line:90%
by us before we incarnated.

00:33:02.340 --> 00:33:03.790 align:middle line:90%
Do you believe that?

00:33:03.790 --> 00:33:08.360 align:middle line:10%
How many times have you
solidly, irrefutably recognized

00:33:08.360 --> 00:33:11.530 align:middle line:10%
or experienced this?

00:33:11.530 --> 00:33:14.600 align:middle line:10%
"Life Between Life" inspired
me to write my second book.

00:33:14.600 --> 00:33:17.400 align:middle line:10%
Its title is
"Junior Cosmic Egg."

00:33:17.400 --> 00:33:19.160 align:middle line:10%
And it is the story
of a cosmic egg

00:33:19.160 --> 00:33:23.410 align:middle line:10%
named Junior, who wants to grow
up to become his own universe.

00:33:23.410 --> 00:33:26.400 align:middle line:84%
During this time, I was leading
a children's Sunday School

00:33:26.400 --> 00:33:28.150 align:middle line:84%
at a religious science
church in Nashville

00:33:28.150 --> 00:33:31.880 align:middle line:84%
and intended "Junior"
to be a children's book.

00:33:31.880 --> 00:33:34.870 align:middle line:84%
I hoped that the story of
this tiny egg realizing

00:33:34.870 --> 00:33:37.750 align:middle line:84%
the unlimited potential
packed inside him

00:33:37.750 --> 00:33:40.210 align:middle line:84%
would inspire kids of
all ages to explore

00:33:40.210 --> 00:33:44.450 align:middle line:84%
the power within themselves
and our astonishing universe.

00:33:44.450 --> 00:33:46.970 align:middle line:84%
I envisioned a children's
metaphysical workshop

00:33:46.970 --> 00:33:49.120 align:middle line:84%
around "Junior," in
which he would teach kids

00:33:49.120 --> 00:33:51.720 align:middle line:84%
the lost language of
symbolism as a way

00:33:51.720 --> 00:33:54.410 align:middle line:84%
to unite the children
of the world.

00:33:54.410 --> 00:33:57.070 align:middle line:84%
I hand-illustrated hundreds
of copies of this book

00:33:57.070 --> 00:33:59.010 align:middle line:84%
and gave out Junior
Cosmic Egg Awards

00:33:59.010 --> 00:34:01.480 align:middle line:84%
for outstanding
achievement in the service

00:34:01.480 --> 00:34:04.030 align:middle line:84%
to the transformation
of the human race.

00:34:04.030 --> 00:34:07.550 align:middle line:84%
Al Gore, Oprah Winfrey,
Don Henley, Dr. John Lilly

00:34:07.550 --> 00:34:10.199 align:middle line:90%
were among my awardees.

00:34:10.199 --> 00:34:11.880 align:middle line:84%
I would surprise
them at public events

00:34:11.880 --> 00:34:14.510 align:middle line:84%
with their award for
their achievements.

00:34:14.510 --> 00:34:16.630 align:middle line:84%
And with "Junior
Cosmic Egg" in hand,

00:34:16.630 --> 00:34:20.110 align:middle line:84%
I set off lecturing on the
Whole Life Expo circuit.

00:34:20.110 --> 00:34:22.760 align:middle line:84%
My topic was "Kids and
the New Consciousness."

00:34:22.760 --> 00:34:24.929 align:middle line:84%
And I'd gone about
collecting stories

00:34:24.929 --> 00:34:28.699 align:middle line:84%
of children's interactions
with angels, extraterrestrials,

00:34:28.699 --> 00:34:33.409 align:middle line:84%
and even Jesus, most of which
were absolutely astounding.

00:34:33.409 --> 00:34:35.090 align:middle line:84%
And it led me to
realize that there's

00:34:35.090 --> 00:34:39.820 align:middle line:84%
a whole lot more going on in
our world than most realize.

00:34:39.820 --> 00:34:42.370 align:middle line:84%
Often, it was the
parents who contributed

00:34:42.370 --> 00:34:44.380 align:middle line:90%
the most amazing stories.

00:34:44.380 --> 00:34:46.770 align:middle line:84%
It turns out that they,
too, had experienced

00:34:46.770 --> 00:34:48.190 align:middle line:90%
these otherworldly beings.

00:34:48.190 --> 00:34:50.747 align:middle line:84%
But being children
of the '50s and '60s,

00:34:50.747 --> 00:34:53.330 align:middle line:84%
they weren't able to tell their
parents about these encounters

00:34:53.330 --> 00:34:54.996 align:middle line:84%
for fear that they
wouldn't believe them

00:34:54.996 --> 00:34:57.139 align:middle line:90%
or they'd think they're weird.

00:34:57.139 --> 00:34:59.220 align:middle line:84%
But our world has
shifted dramatically

00:34:59.220 --> 00:35:01.040 align:middle line:90%
in the past 25 years.

00:35:01.040 --> 00:35:03.510 align:middle line:84%
Now, angels and
extraterrestrials

00:35:03.510 --> 00:35:05.270 align:middle line:90%
are the new normal.

00:35:05.270 --> 00:35:07.320 align:middle line:90%
Our universe has expanded.

00:35:07.320 --> 00:35:10.730 align:middle line:84%
Our collective
soul is awakening.

00:35:10.730 --> 00:35:14.050 align:middle line:84%
We are ascending and getting
closer to discovering

00:35:14.050 --> 00:35:17.510 align:middle line:90%
the lost science of the soul.

00:35:17.510 --> 00:35:19.510 align:middle line:10%
"Junior Cosmic
Egg" introduced me

00:35:19.510 --> 00:35:23.830 align:middle line:10%
to a whole new world of
mythology I never knew existed.

00:35:23.830 --> 00:35:26.460 align:middle line:84%
I learned that for
thousands of years,

00:35:26.460 --> 00:35:30.580 align:middle line:84%
the cosmic egg had
symbolized the soul,

00:35:30.580 --> 00:35:35.480 align:middle line:84%
going back 7,000 years to
the incredible Algarve egg.

00:35:35.480 --> 00:35:39.730 align:middle line:84%
The ancients in all
lands revered the egg

00:35:39.730 --> 00:35:43.120 align:middle line:84%
as the symbol of
regeneration and immortality

00:35:43.120 --> 00:35:46.940 align:middle line:90%
in the galaxy and the soul.

00:35:46.940 --> 00:35:50.470 align:middle line:84%
To alchemists, it was the
philosophical egg, guarded

00:35:50.470 --> 00:35:52.840 align:middle line:90%
by the serpent or dragon.

00:35:52.840 --> 00:35:55.870 align:middle line:84%
There's that
reptilian code again.

00:35:55.870 --> 00:35:59.110 align:middle line:84%
Since the paleolithic
times, the beginning of life

00:35:59.110 --> 00:36:02.840 align:middle line:84%
has been described as the
hatching of a cosmic egg,

00:36:02.840 --> 00:36:07.090 align:middle line:84%
laid by a sacred great
mother bird, the golden goose

00:36:07.090 --> 00:36:10.920 align:middle line:84%
or ghoost as in Holy
Ghost of fairy tales

00:36:10.920 --> 00:36:15.820 align:middle line:84%
that drops the egg into the
waters of space or chaos.

00:36:15.820 --> 00:36:17.715 align:middle line:84%
Isn't it interesting
that Laniakea,

00:36:17.715 --> 00:36:22.650 align:middle line:84%
the "immeasurable heaven"
resembles a bird in flight?

00:36:22.650 --> 00:36:25.840 align:middle line:84%
This is a bird-shaped jug
from Phaistos on ancient Crete

00:36:25.840 --> 00:36:29.450 align:middle line:90%
from around 2000 BC.

00:36:29.450 --> 00:36:33.620 align:middle line:84%
Within its body are
spirals and eggs.

00:36:33.620 --> 00:36:37.220 align:middle line:84%
It tells the story of
how this egg cracked open

00:36:37.220 --> 00:36:39.720 align:middle line:90%
and all life appeared.

00:36:39.720 --> 00:36:44.130 align:middle line:84%
Cosmic energy, or essence, the
seed from which all life began,

00:36:44.130 --> 00:36:47.220 align:middle line:84%
including our souls,
sprang into existence

00:36:47.220 --> 00:36:50.600 align:middle line:84%
and fanned out in
spiraling ways.

00:36:50.600 --> 00:36:52.940 align:middle line:84%
It's incredible that
it looks astonishingly

00:36:52.940 --> 00:36:56.970 align:middle line:84%
similar to the spiraling funnel
of emissions NASA discovered

00:36:56.970 --> 00:37:00.210 align:middle line:84%
coming from the supermassive
black hole buried

00:37:00.210 --> 00:37:04.130 align:middle line:84%
in the heart of
our galaxy in 2010.

00:37:04.130 --> 00:37:06.910 align:middle line:84%
To ancient philosophers,
the question

00:37:06.910 --> 00:37:10.120 align:middle line:84%
about which came first, the
chicken or the egg, also

00:37:10.120 --> 00:37:13.960 align:middle line:84%
evoke questions of how life,
the soul, and the universe

00:37:13.960 --> 00:37:15.650 align:middle line:90%
in general began.

00:37:15.650 --> 00:37:19.300 align:middle line:84%
To Aristotle, they
both always existed.

00:37:19.300 --> 00:37:22.240 align:middle line:84%
For Plato, before everything
appeared on Earth,

00:37:22.240 --> 00:37:26.970 align:middle line:84%
it first existed in
spirit as a thought.

00:37:26.970 --> 00:37:30.210 align:middle line:84%
Speaking of Plato, I have
traced his story of Atlantis

00:37:30.210 --> 00:37:32.880 align:middle line:84%
to the temple of Horus
at Edfu in Egypt, where

00:37:32.880 --> 00:37:35.770 align:middle line:84%
we find that the
Edfu creation text,

00:37:35.770 --> 00:37:38.340 align:middle line:90%
and also to Dendera, Egypt.

00:37:38.340 --> 00:37:40.620 align:middle line:84%
These texts say that
in the beginning

00:37:40.620 --> 00:37:44.900 align:middle line:84%
of Egyptian cosmology, there is
the cosmic egg that emerged out

00:37:44.900 --> 00:37:47.690 align:middle line:84%
of the spirit
waters of creation.

00:37:47.690 --> 00:37:50.070 align:middle line:10%
Blue light beings
with bird heads,

00:37:50.070 --> 00:37:54.400 align:middle line:10%
bearing some kind of technology,
emerged from the cosmic egg

00:37:54.400 --> 00:37:58.660 align:middle line:10%
and created the island of the
egg, out of which emerged,

00:37:58.660 --> 00:38:04.070 align:middle line:10%
or hatched, the first
human civilization.

00:38:04.070 --> 00:38:07.110 align:middle line:84%
The symbol of the egg in
creation myths is ubiquitous.

00:38:07.110 --> 00:38:10.170 align:middle line:84%
It's everywhere
throughout the world.

00:38:10.170 --> 00:38:13.200 align:middle line:84%
In the Indian knowledge system,
for example, the cosmic egg

00:38:13.200 --> 00:38:18.480 align:middle line:84%
is known as Hiranyagarbha,
meaning a golden hued womb.

00:38:18.480 --> 00:38:21.390 align:middle line:84%
And the Big Bang of
creation is expressed

00:38:21.390 --> 00:38:26.820 align:middle line:84%
as Brahmanda Visphotak,
or universal explosion.

00:38:26.820 --> 00:38:29.860 align:middle line:84%
In the Kalevala, the
Finnish national epic,

00:38:29.860 --> 00:38:31.850 align:middle line:84%
there's a myth of the
world being created

00:38:31.850 --> 00:38:34.500 align:middle line:90%
from the fragments of an egg.

00:38:34.500 --> 00:38:37.130 align:middle line:84%
And according to Chinese
mythology, in the beginning

00:38:37.130 --> 00:38:39.120 align:middle line:84%
there was nothing
in the universe

00:38:39.120 --> 00:38:42.200 align:middle line:90%
except a formless chaos.

00:38:42.200 --> 00:38:46.040 align:middle line:84%
Then, this chaos coalesced
into a cosmic egg

00:38:46.040 --> 00:38:50.260 align:middle line:84%
for about 18,000 years before
breaking in half to create

00:38:50.260 --> 00:38:53.700 align:middle line:90%
the sky and the earth.

00:38:53.700 --> 00:38:59.490 align:middle line:84%
The idea that our souls
came from or is a cosmic egg

00:38:59.490 --> 00:39:02.690 align:middle line:84%
is actually shared by the Celts,
the Greeks, the Egyptians,

00:39:02.690 --> 00:39:05.670 align:middle line:84%
Phoenicians, Canaanites,
Tibetans, Hindus, Vietnamese,

00:39:05.670 --> 00:39:09.550 align:middle line:84%
Chinese, Russians, Central
Americans, and Indonesians.

00:39:09.550 --> 00:39:12.730 align:middle line:84%
It suggests to me
that this concept was

00:39:12.730 --> 00:39:17.250 align:middle line:84%
a self-evident truth
or that someone

00:39:17.250 --> 00:39:21.340 align:middle line:84%
had given this code symbol,
this code of the soul,

00:39:21.340 --> 00:39:25.690 align:middle line:84%
to these varied peoples through
some form of revelation,

00:39:25.690 --> 00:39:30.060 align:middle line:84%
perhaps by some form of ethereal
spirit or wandering missionary

00:39:30.060 --> 00:39:32.710 align:middle line:90%
or missionaries.

00:39:32.710 --> 00:39:36.610 align:middle line:84%
In their art, the Mayans
were among several cultures

00:39:36.610 --> 00:39:38.450 align:middle line:84%
that used what we
call the letter

00:39:38.450 --> 00:39:44.790 align:middle line:84%
G to symbolize the egg creator,
the essence, and the Milky Way.

00:39:44.790 --> 00:39:48.640 align:middle line:84%
When the G appears on the walls
of Mayan temples, pyramids,

00:39:48.640 --> 00:39:52.160 align:middle line:84%
sculptures, or in their codices,
says Mayan ceremonial leader

00:39:52.160 --> 00:39:56.260 align:middle line:84%
Hunbatz Men, it's a code
symbol for the secret mysteries

00:39:56.260 --> 00:40:01.520 align:middle line:84%
of the science or religion of
the Milky Way, the cosmic eggs.

00:40:01.520 --> 00:40:07.450 align:middle line:84%
How the Mayans knew a galaxy
was G-shaped is unknown.

00:40:07.450 --> 00:40:12.750 align:middle line:84%
But the Maya were not alone in
symbolizing the galaxy by a G.

00:40:12.750 --> 00:40:16.380 align:middle line:10%
This Neolithic design depicts
two human figures consisting

00:40:16.380 --> 00:40:19.590 align:middle line:10%
of two triangles in
almond-shaped enclosures

00:40:19.590 --> 00:40:23.720 align:middle line:10%
on either side of a
meandering belt of G's.

00:40:23.720 --> 00:40:25.340 align:middle line:84%
The primitive
artist who rendered

00:40:25.340 --> 00:40:28.390 align:middle line:84%
this scene was supposed to have
been barely capable of playing

00:40:28.390 --> 00:40:32.200 align:middle line:84%
with sticks and stones, yet
from a modern point of view,

00:40:32.200 --> 00:40:34.980 align:middle line:84%
its narrative suggests
knowledge of wormholes

00:40:34.980 --> 00:40:38.750 align:middle line:90%
linking multiple galaxies.

00:40:38.750 --> 00:40:41.020 align:middle line:10%
It appears to me
that this figure

00:40:41.020 --> 00:40:43.850 align:middle line:10%
started at one end of
the belt of galaxies

00:40:43.850 --> 00:40:49.850 align:middle line:10%
and starwalked through the
other four G's, or galaxies.

00:40:49.850 --> 00:40:53.310 align:middle line:84%
For thousands of years, the
clockwise spiral ideogram

00:40:53.310 --> 00:40:57.010 align:middle line:84%
has been strongly associated
with water, power,

00:40:57.010 --> 00:40:59.110 align:middle line:90%
and outgoing energy.

00:40:59.110 --> 00:41:01.550 align:middle line:84%
Starting from the
middle, it forms

00:41:01.550 --> 00:41:05.970 align:middle line:84%
a G. Its mirror or twin
image or inversion,

00:41:05.970 --> 00:41:09.170 align:middle line:84%
the spiral in its
counterclockwise rotation,

00:41:09.170 --> 00:41:11.380 align:middle line:84%
appeared at approximately
the same time.

00:41:11.380 --> 00:41:15.850 align:middle line:84%
And it happens to be an Egyptian
hieroglyph for "thread."

00:41:15.850 --> 00:41:18.300 align:middle line:90%
Both symbols resemble a fetus.

00:41:18.300 --> 00:41:24.500 align:middle line:84%
And a similar Chinese ideogram
means return or homecoming.

00:41:24.500 --> 00:41:28.220 align:middle line:84%
To the Mayans, the
G also represented

00:41:28.220 --> 00:41:32.120 align:middle line:90%
the concept of zero, an egg.

00:41:32.120 --> 00:41:35.370 align:middle line:84%
And the egg happens to be
a modern scientific symbol

00:41:35.370 --> 00:41:38.290 align:middle line:90%
meaning galaxy.

00:41:38.290 --> 00:41:41.600 align:middle line:84%
Going deeper, the
G shape is also

00:41:41.600 --> 00:41:44.060 align:middle line:84%
the musical notation
for a whole note,

00:41:44.060 --> 00:41:47.340 align:middle line:90%
which also resembles an egg.

00:41:47.340 --> 00:41:50.870 align:middle line:84%
As this sacred note
rises within us,

00:41:50.870 --> 00:41:53.970 align:middle line:84%
we transform, is
the message here.

00:41:53.970 --> 00:41:56.510 align:middle line:84%
In ancient Egypt,
the creator god Ptah

00:41:56.510 --> 00:41:59.505 align:middle line:84%
was a potter who
fashioned the human body

00:41:59.505 --> 00:42:02.610 align:middle line:90%
by potting it like an egg.

00:42:02.610 --> 00:42:07.200 align:middle line:84%
Mithras, the Roman god,
was born from a cosmic egg.

00:42:07.200 --> 00:42:09.915 align:middle line:84%
And the Magi of
the Christ story,

00:42:09.915 --> 00:42:14.160 align:middle line:84%
knew the secret of the
mystical cosmic egg.

00:42:14.160 --> 00:42:16.620 align:middle line:84%
One of the earliest
icons of Mary

00:42:16.620 --> 00:42:20.520 align:middle line:84%
shows Jesus in a glowing
transparent cosmic egg

00:42:20.520 --> 00:42:22.670 align:middle line:90%
in her womb.

00:42:22.670 --> 00:42:25.540 align:middle line:84%
This image has tremendous
spiritual power now

00:42:25.540 --> 00:42:30.150 align:middle line:84%
that we know we are all
considered to be cosmic eggs.

00:42:30.150 --> 00:42:32.500 align:middle line:84%
Until the eighth
century, the Christ child

00:42:32.500 --> 00:42:37.500 align:middle line:84%
was shown in a cosmic
egg, in this case, blue.

00:42:37.500 --> 00:42:40.350 align:middle line:10%
And as we will explore
in detail later,

00:42:40.350 --> 00:42:46.400 align:middle line:10%
the blue egg or blue sphere is
actually a bubble for transport

00:42:46.400 --> 00:42:50.730 align:middle line:10%
and is described by shamans
as a sort of quantum egg

00:42:50.730 --> 00:42:56.020 align:middle line:10%
that the soul uses to phase
in and out of our reality.

00:42:56.020 --> 00:43:00.730 align:middle line:84%
Finally, our transfiguration
or change in form,

00:43:00.730 --> 00:43:04.860 align:middle line:84%
as occurred to Jesus, is
symbolized by the egg of light

00:43:04.860 --> 00:43:09.610 align:middle line:84%
surrounding Jesus during
the transfiguration when

00:43:09.610 --> 00:43:14.740 align:middle line:90%
His body became a star gate.

00:43:14.740 --> 00:43:18.170 align:middle line:84%
The egg of light is also
seen in the ascension.

00:43:18.170 --> 00:43:23.085 align:middle line:84%
The resurrected Christ is often
enthroned in a cosmic egg.

00:43:23.085 --> 00:43:26.430 align:middle line:84%
It is the Merkabah
egg, the throne

00:43:26.430 --> 00:43:30.370 align:middle line:84%
or chariot of the soul
of Jewish mysticism.

00:43:30.370 --> 00:43:33.460 align:middle line:84%
And, according to
tradition, some time

00:43:33.460 --> 00:43:36.210 align:middle line:84%
after the Resurrection
of Christ,

00:43:36.210 --> 00:43:41.290 align:middle line:84%
Mary Magdalene went to Rome
to see emperor Tiberius Caesar

00:43:41.290 --> 00:43:45.720 align:middle line:84%
and announced to him that
Christ had risen from the dead

00:43:45.720 --> 00:43:49.630 align:middle line:84%
and explained how
it all took place.

00:43:49.630 --> 00:43:52.210 align:middle line:84%
After she finished,
Tiberius noticed

00:43:52.210 --> 00:43:55.465 align:middle line:84%
a man next to him
holding a basket of eggs.

00:43:55.465 --> 00:44:00.170 align:middle line:84%
And Tiberius challenged Mary
that if what she said was true,

00:44:00.170 --> 00:44:01.910 align:middle line:84%
then the white
eggs in the basket

00:44:01.910 --> 00:44:05.090 align:middle line:90%
should be turned into red eggs.

00:44:05.090 --> 00:44:10.190 align:middle line:84%
Suddenly, the eggs turned red,
leaving Caesar astonished.

00:44:10.190 --> 00:44:15.520 align:middle line:84%
And this is why we
decorate eggs on Easter.

00:44:15.520 --> 00:44:20.620 align:middle line:84%
And the appearance of Christ
is symbolized by the egg.

00:44:20.620 --> 00:44:25.150 align:middle line:84%
Finally, it is upon this
blue cosmic egg or sphere

00:44:25.150 --> 00:44:29.600 align:middle line:84%
that Christ will appear on
Judgment Day or the Second

00:44:29.600 --> 00:44:30.690 align:middle line:90%
Coming.

00:44:30.690 --> 00:44:36.440 align:middle line:84%
As we see here, blue angels
compose the cosmic egg.

00:44:36.440 --> 00:44:39.390 align:middle line:84%
So do such similar
origin stories

00:44:39.390 --> 00:44:43.850 align:middle line:84%
exist simply because all life
on Earth starts from an egg,

00:44:43.850 --> 00:44:45.740 align:middle line:84%
even though early
humans presumably

00:44:45.740 --> 00:44:49.350 align:middle line:84%
did not know that we,
too, begin life in an egg?

00:44:49.350 --> 00:44:51.700 align:middle line:84%
Or might it reveal
that our ancestors

00:44:51.700 --> 00:44:55.060 align:middle line:84%
had a greater knowledge
of our soul, our world,

00:44:55.060 --> 00:44:58.100 align:middle line:84%
and our universe
than we imagine?

00:44:58.100 --> 00:45:01.570 align:middle line:84%
Might they have known that
our soul is a cosmic egg,

00:45:01.570 --> 00:45:04.720 align:middle line:84%
and that one day,
we, too, will ascend

00:45:04.720 --> 00:45:07.810 align:middle line:90%
to the stars in a cosmic egg?

00:45:07.810 --> 00:45:09.890 align:middle line:90%
Until next time, be humble.

00:45:09.890 --> 00:45:11.720 align:middle line:90%
Let your light shine.

00:45:11.720 --> 00:45:12.970 align:middle line:90%
Namaste.

00:45:12.970 --> 00:45:14.290 align:middle line:90%
This is William Henry.

00:45:14.290 --> 00:45:16.580 align:middle line:90%
Thank you for watching.

00:45:16.580 --> 00:45:31.862 align:middle line:90%